StMinuitVertexMaker:

Minuit based vertex finder.  See StVertexFinder.h for details

Inputs:
StEvent

Switches:  
UseVertexConstraint(x0,y0,dxdz,dydz,weight) -- Swithces vertex finder to 1D mode for pp

CTBforSeed() -- require CTB match for tracks used to find vertex seed

use_ITTF  --  use ITTF tracks (checks encoded method)


Output:

No output, but fit results can be accessed from StVertexFinder.result()